\par
\f2\bullet  The easiest trick to memorize the 7 OSI layers in 10 seconds\par
\bullet  How hackers attack each OSI layer in real life\par
\bullet  How tools like Kali Linux use the OSI model\par
\bullet  Real examples of OSI model attacks used by hackers\par
