5\tab sessions\tab session hijacking\par
6\tab encryption\tab SSL stripping\par
7\tab applications\tab SQL injection\par
\par
\f3\u9989?\f0  Important cybersecurity tip\par
\par
Most modern cyber attacks happen mainly at:\par
\par
Layer 3\par
\par
Layer 4\par
\par
Layer 7\lang9\par
